## Skill Router

Match user intent against triggers; load **one** skill on demand. Don't pre-load.

{{SKILL_ROUTER}}

**Priority:** explicit `/slash` invocation wins. Else first-match wins. Else, no skill load.

## Memory Protocol

See `MEMORY.md` (generated index — keep in sync with every file under `memory/`) for the always-loaded index. Bucket files under `memory/{user,feedback,project,reference}/` (one fact per file, `[[wikilinks]]`) load on demand by topic. Logs live in `logs/`, never in `memory/`.

{{MEMORY_PROTOCOL}}

